data.title: Best Place Immobilien
data.meta_description: Whether for singles, couples or families - in peaceful and family-friendly surroundings, a new home is born in the quiet and screened area facing Treskowstraße. The total of 165 apartments of Quartier 49 are modern and efficiently cut as well as equipped to a high standard. Each apartment has its own individual charm and offers a high-level living experience. Whether with real wood parquet flooring made of high-quality oak, en-suite bathrooms or south-facing balconies - Quartier 49 makes living dreams come true and turns your home into your new place to be.
data.text: By ordering the exposé, you declare that you have taken note of our privacy policy. The sale of the property shown here is not carried out by Best Place Immobilien GmbH & Co. KG as the operator of this website, but by Best Place Living GmbH. The processing of data for the purpose of contacting you and sending you the exposé is carried out exclusively by Best Place Living GmbH. You will receive the corresponding data protection information when responding to your inquiry.
